OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather cloudy day with
OL,6,Foccasional rain, some heavy and
OL,7,Fthundery rain at times especially in
OL,8,Fthe south. Some drier spells of
OL,9,Fweather too. Warm and humid.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FAny showers dying out but
OL,12,Fquite a cloudy evening in places with
OL,13,Fsome mist and fog possible. Winds
OL,14,Fstrengthening overnight and feeling
OL,15,Fquite muggy and warm.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FA bright and mostly dry
OL,18,Fstart to the weekend but warm and
OL,19,Fwindy, some showers developing in the
OL,20,Fwest in the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
